-- U.K. Foreign Office Says British National Has Been Abducted in Afghanistan
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2010-09-26T20:24:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/u-k-foreign-office-says-british-national-has-been-abducted-in-afghanistan.html
A British national has been
abducted in Afghanistan, the U.K.’s Foreign Office said after it
earlier confirmed one was missing in the country.  “We are working closely with all the relevant local
authorities,” a spokeswoman for the Foreign Office said by
telephone. “We are also in touch with the family and are
providing consular assistance.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Livesey at 
 blivesey@bloomberg.net  